snippet.title: Dev Diaries: World Generation
snippet.description: Join Agnes, Henrik, and Jasper to learn more about the caves, cave biomes, and mountains in the Caves & Cliffs Update! Focussing specifically on world generation, they discuss what inspired the new features, how they include different player styles, and which real-world rules they decided to keep, and which ones they bent. We also learn about the spaghetti caves and cheese caves, so you risk walking away both inspired and hungry!
